divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving past this high tech lab near Cold Spring Harbor when I saw a UFO hovering in the parking lot in the lab to my right. The light was bright and pulsing and I felt compelled to park my car in the middle of rte 25A and walk towards the light. There were these rat-like creatures that reached into my head with imaginary fists and permanently shut my mouth. Now I can not talk. I am terrified. Will this ever get better???
